      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p><em>From <a href="https://code.google.com/u/109067824594513388759/">thilo.mu...@gmail.com</a> on May 28, 2010 09:00:21</em></p>

<p>Currently the MapView can only display the map according to the orientation<br>
of the device (portrait/landscape). It should be possible to freely rotate<br>
the map, for example based on the compass sensor.</p>

<p><em>Original issue: <a href="http://code.google.com/p/mapsforge/issues/detail?id=7">http://code.google.com/p/mapsforge/issues/detail?id=7</a></em></p>
